WEBVTT

00:00:09.240 --> 00:00:11.920
<v Audio Description> A man drops his computer mouse off the desk.

00:00:11.940 --> 00:00:14.240
<v Audio Description> The computer mouse no longer works.

00:00:20.140 --> 00:00:23.600
<v Audio Description> A woman with her arm in a sling is typing on a keyboard

00:00:26.120 --> 00:00:29.520
<v Audio Description> but the website requires the use of a mouse to select the date.

00:00:29.520 --> 00:00:32.960
<v Audio Description> A man with a wheelchair is using a mouth-stick to type.

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:38.060
<v Audio Description> The man with the wheelchair also cannot use the site.

00:00:44.740 --> 00:00:48.360
<v Audio Description> He switches to a different website that allows typing the date.
